title: ⚽🔥 Top Betting Picks – World Cup Qualifiers 2026 Edition
content_md:
We’re back with sharp betting insights for today’s qualifiers & friendlies 📊🎯💰

1️⃣ Norway 🇳🇴 vs Moldova 🇲🇩
The Nordic team is led by Haaland ⚡ and Ødegaard 🎩 against a weak Moldova side.
✅ Pick: Norway to WIN 🏆🇳🇴💪

2️⃣ Serbia 🇷🇸 vs England 🏴
A tight clash ahead 🤜🤛. England, improving under Tuchel 📈, should keep it low-scoring.
✅ Pick: Under 2 Goals ⚽🔒🏴

3️⃣ Venezuela 🇻🇪 vs Colombia 🇨🇴
La Vinotinto will fight hard 🔥 to stay alive in the playoff race, while Colombia is already qualified.
✅ Pick: Venezuela to WIN 🏆🇻🇪🎉

4️⃣ Wales 🏴 vs Canada 🇨🇦 (Friendly Match)
Canada continues strong in their friendlies 🍁💪, while Wales looks weaker in recent outings.
✅ Pick: Canada to WIN 🏆🇨🇦⚡
